{
  "abstract": "Despite the promise of climate-smart agriculture (CSA) to improve food security in South Asia, most CSA practices and\r\ntechnologies have not been widely adopted. We identify the key barriers to CSA adoption in South Asia and suggest strategies to overcome them to increase CSA adoption at scale.",
